content.rendered:
Air Freight

We offers a wide variety of cargo air charter services around the world.

Excel Cargo has the global air charter services expertise you need for your most critical cargo shipments.

Excel Cargo specializes in sensitive, time-critical air transportation logistics and shipments that require a high degree of personal attention through our network of handling agents with unmatched expertise. We have no restrictions based on size, weight or dollar value and can provide door to door service for your air shipments.

We have all the world-class international logistics expertise and resources you need without the weighty bureaucratic infrastructure of a large company. Given the urgency of your shipments, our air transportation logistics solutions can pick up within an hour of your call in most locations. We guarantee the chain-of-custody process from point-of-pickup to delivery and offer the latest possible pickup for earliest delivery. All in flight tracking and communication is done person-to-person.

High-Value Air Cargo Transporation

Air transportation logistiocs is a vital component of many international organizations. It is essential to managing the flow of goods, energy, information, services, and even people from start to finish. This makes professional logistical, such as Excel Cargo white glove service support essential.  Our logistics specialists will help integrate information, transport, inventory, storage, handling, and packaging — all while keeping costs to a minimum.

Tailored Air Transportation Logistics Solutions

Excel Cargo Logistics is a leading provider of international freight forwarding services, including air, ocean, ground, and rail options. We offer the scale and scope of services to meet the budget and schedule requirements of each customer.
